snippet: Serena Williams stormed into the U.S. Open quarter-finals in record-smashing style on Monday by easing past Kazakhstan's Yaroslava Shvedova 6-2 6-3 to claim her record 308th grand slam match win....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams stormed into the U.S. Open quarter-finals in record-smashing style on Monday by easing past Kazakhstan's Yaroslava Shvedova 6-2 6-3 to claim her record 308th grand slam match win.

headline.print_headline: Serena Storms Into Quarters in Record-Smashing Style
headline.main: Serena Storms Into Quarters in Record-Smashing Style
